params.name: filepath
params.description: path of file to construct vocabulary.

params.name: unk_token
params.description: special token for unknown token. If no need, it alsocould be None. Defaults to None.

params.name: pad_token
params.description: special token for padding token. If no need, it alsocould be None. Defaults to None.

params.name: bos_token
params.description: special token for bos token. If no need, it alsocould be None. Defaults to None.

params.name: eos_token
params.description: special token for eos token. If no need, it alsocould be None. Defaults to None.
